      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776759578000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "青数\n企业的数据治理与能力管理中台\n把分散数据整理成统一口径的数据资产，\n再把这些资产发布成 Tool、Skill、Agent。",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
